<template>
  <mainslot>
    <template v-slot:topName>
      张三
    </template>
    <template v-slot:topSlot>
      <router-link to="/">个人信息</router-link>
      <router-link to="/">退出</router-link>
    </template>


    <template v-slot:mainSlot>
      <el-form ref="form" :model="form" label-width="80px" @submit.native.prevent="saveArticle">
        <el-form-item label="留言标题">
          <el-input v-model="form.title"></el-input>
        </el-form-item>
        <el-form-item label="留言内容">
          <el-input v-model="form.page"></el-input>
        </el-form-item>
        <el-form-item>
          <el-button type="primary" native-type="submit">立即创建</el-button>
          <el-button @click="articleCancel">取消</el-button>
        </el-form-item>
      </el-form>

    </template>
  </mainslot>
</template>

<script>
import mainslot from "@/components/repeat/Mainslot";
export default {

  name: "name",
  components: {
    mainslot,
  },

  data() {
    return {
      form: {
        title: '',
        page:'',
      }
    }
  },
  methods: {
    saveArticle() {
      console.log(this.form);
    },
    articleCancel(){
      this.form.title='';
      this.form.page='';
      console.log(this.form);
    }
  },
}

</script>

<style scoped>


</style>
